msgstr "已导入，正在刷新…"

msgid "Import failed"
msgstr "导入失败"

msgid "Advanced / Manual Mode"
msgstr "高级 / 手动模式"

msgid "Edit config.dae directly. Saving the form above regenerates the file and overwrites changes made here."
msgstr "直接编辑 config.dae。上方表单保存会重新生成文件并覆盖这里的改动。"

